  "title": "docs(faq): Add explanation on default filters",
  "body": "Following #1026 I also added an entry on how to set default filters on\nthe first loading of instantsearch. This question often pop ups in\nsupport and we were never really explaining how to do it.\n\nI tried to keep it as simple as possible for most cases when you\nalready have a widget in place on that specific attribute, and only\nneed to set default values.\n\nI also explained how to do it on attributes on which you do not have\na widget, with a bit more config.\n\nLet me know what you think\n\n![image](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/283419/15481511/aa76c996-20df-11e6-8d74-c2384b0d593b.png)\n",
